{"tid":2337859,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"星島900名員工下月起放無薪假 每月4天為期3個月","createTime":"2020-12-23T15:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T16:55:14.000Z","uid":185631,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b0c38e74a4b6b4b82adc5119942c9645f0861a","tid":2337859,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:02:09.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp9gc6rz%2Ba6PLwHdujBQ9FQE%3D&h=6805fdb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】星島新聞集團逾900名員工下月起每月須放4天無薪假，為期3個月。該集團今日(23日)向全體員工發通告指，本港新冠肺炎疫情越趨嚴重，重創本港經濟及各行各業，「對媒體行業的打擊更為極大」，管理層估計經濟環境短期內難以改善，為確保集團長遠穩健，故提出「無薪假的暫時安排」。<br />\n<br />\n根據保就業計劃秘書處資料顯示，星島新聞集團的總公司「SING TAO MANAGEMENT SERVICES LIMITED」在第1期及第2期的保就業計劃，分別獲批2,542萬港元及2,569萬港元，合共逾半億港元，兩期的承諾受薪僱員同為993人。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，星島新聞集團上半年度虧損顯著增加，該集團截至今年6月底止的半年錄得虧損達6,129萬港元，較去年同期的虧損768萬港元，擴大6.98倍。星島新聞集團亦於今年2月6日結束澳洲的業務，其澳洲子公司需要清盤，該集團解釋指是因應經營環境而作出商業調整的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Qo1FGbDFCaCmEI5fju9ipA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/onccinstantnews.com/58c934ff58b8a473a283221a5325356b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQo1FGbDFCaCmEI5fju9ipA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F58c934ff58b8a473a283221a5325356b&h=3da67b36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ecae2c6c50125cf19bd9a13f7f1a5413fa2b9bf","tid":2337859,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:08:21.000Z","msg":"打藍媒工抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d624cbc82006a46096196153d4fd3fd7a5a2be","tid":2337859,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T15:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgm